  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Aesthetic Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop long-term client relationships while upholding a positive and professional brand image.</li></ul><ul><li>Conduct professional consultations on aesthetic, facial, and skincare solutions for clients.</li></ul><ul><li>Introduce products, services, and treatments to customers.</li></ul><ul><li>Evaluate clients’ concerns and recommend suitable treatments in alignment with their needs and the doctor’s guidance.</li></ul><ul><li>Consistently achieve goals set by the company.</li></ul><ul><li>Deliver a high standard of customer care throughout every client interaction.</li></ul><ul><li>Follow up with clients on post-treatment progress and schedule reminders for upcoming appointments.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Strong sales-oriented mindset with a proven track record of meeting targets.</li></ul><ul><li>Customer-focused, driven, and motivated to achieve results while providing excellent service.</li></ul><ul><li>A collaborative team player with strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li></ul><ul><li>Have to work on Saturdays (half day).</li></ul><ul><li>Able to thrive in a fast-paced environment.</li></ul><ul><li>Knowledge of the beauty and aesthetics industry will be beneficial.</li></ul><ul><li>Previous experience in aesthetics, beauty, or a related field is an added advantage.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Performance-based bonuses and incentives</li></ul><ul><li>Staff treatment privileges and employee discounts</li></ul><ul><li>Ongoing training and career advancement opportunities</li></ul><ul><li>Incentive-based travel rewards</li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates please kindly include in your CV:</strong><br />-  Photo of yourself<br />-  Current and expected salary<br /></p><p></p>",
